orecchiette (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=low
  * Bumped version to 0.1, as Orecchiette appears to be usable.  Will try to start cleaning it up for release to the Extras repository.
  * A new dialog box for editing the filename format string has been added, again thanks to Peter Pichler.

 -- John Pietrzak <jpietrzak8@gmail.com>  Thu, 10 Apr 2014 22:48:17 -0400

orecchiette (0.0.5) unstable; urgency=low
  * Courtesy of Peter Pichler, several new features have been added:
  * Audio recording filenames can now be highly customized via a new format string on the preferences form
  * Orecchiette now remembers the audio source used previously and automatically selects it when restarted.
  * Orecchiette can be set to immediately begin recording whenever it is started.

 -- John Pietrzak <jpietrzak8@gmail.com>  Mon, 24 Mar 2014 20:51:38 -0400

